{"id":"639919","title":"首席宠婚365天","writer":"江小湖","dateline":"1563994146","updatetime":"1563994146","isover":"1","filesize":"3823271","linecount":"27569","wordcount":"1263357","imgpath":"https://photos.smugmug.com/photos/i-9zG4ZDv/0/d13a280b/O/i-9zG4ZDv.jpg","hash":"shouxichonghun365tian","urlhash":"lltxt_1352602","sign":"","desc":"小说阅读网2016-07-05VIP完结\n简介：\n      “我们的合约只有365天，今天是最后的期限，再见，叶淮南。”她微笑着，将一纸契约，连带曾经遭受的耻辱，一并还给他。** **“秦安暖，你的唇，我的；你的身体，我的；你的心，我的；从今天起，我买下你的一生，不要让任何男人有机会接近你，否则，杀无赦！”他是冷硬无情的总裁，对她绝对的独占，从不给任何逃避的机会。他百般掠夺，只为给她造少女最美的梦，想逃？绝无可能。 **她的心，终于在他的强取豪夺之下**，可是在决定将真心交付的那一刻却发现了他精心编织的谎言。水晶球破碎，梦醒了，她该何去何从？ **几年后。 “国际知名设计师秦安暖被曝与神秘幕后金主共组家庭”的新闻传到了叶淮南面前，他穿越大半个地球，将她掳走，并冷酷宣告—— “秦安暖，你敢违背我的命令，就要接受惩罚，时间是一辈子，方式由我定。”","hot":"0","num":"0","cid":"170","suggcate":"言情,浪漫言情,穿越,总裁,强取豪夺","suggcids":"170,205,287,293,218,275","notbook":"0","fetchv":"0","lasthot":"0","clicknum":"0","isvip":"1","ish":"0","age":"现代","channel":"女","isqiniu":"0","list":"0,2qb,5pb,96u,ccx,fss,ijy,l4c,o6q,rfj,tz3,xah,102s,132s,15da,17hy,1ad8,1d1b,1fbm,1hsn,1k3n,1m9g,1oaj,1quv,1t20,1v18,1xjh,203p,22po,24up,27eb,29hh,2c1c,2eud,2hba,2jhc,2lh5,2nnn,2qbp,2t6o,2vby,2xi7,3030,32vm,34ti,37dc,39pb,3c63,3ezg,3hxl,3ked,3mzj,3pnk,3rz1,3ukh,3x8v,3zxr,42r5,45dz,4821,4aqq,4cwj,4fwb,4j00,4lc1,4nqe,4q9j,4sys,4vdb,4xjf,4zq3,52a5,54lh,56rz,598t,5bog,5e3n,5gyi,5jhh,5low,5odu,5qy9,5tmd,5vnm,5y3l,60hx,62ul,65tw,68dc,6ahr,6cu3,6ey0,6h7m,6k45,6mib,6p2p,6rsy,6ujl,6wzg,6zu6,71o0,73t5,76ns,78rr,7bll,7ean,7gnf,7j2t,7l4r,7nlp,7pys,7sfe,7uys,7xih,7zwc,82me,84ta,86z1,8962,8bi2,8dv2,8g3m,8ier,8l5n,8n7t,8pgv,8s47,8ucv,8ws2,8zg0,91so,94of,9798,99tt,9cio,9f1f,9hcr,9k8p,9mgp,9p4w,9rhw,9u2e,9wco,9yk3,a1a3,a3jp,a5yc,a8cd,aapz,adab,aff6,ahny,ajn6,alvq,ao50,aquf,atr8,aw7u,ayva,b1ef,b441,b6wi,b9g4,bc89,bexz,bhq7,bkcu,bmq2,bpcm,bsb1,buuu,bxj4,bzwv,c2bq,c4g6,c6v1,c9md,cc4w,cer5,chhf,ck1i,cmlp,cp0p,cs0j,culn,cxas,czws,d2gs,d55r,d80i,dad2,dcxz,dfl5,di4b,dklt,dnb9,dqjq,dtjr,dwf3,dywj,e1mc,e4gz,e6yw,e9lv,ec29,ef7y,ehib,ejmz,emlt,epne,et0a,evwl,eyip,f13s,f4b5